snippet.title: The King of Fighters '97: Global Match (PC) - Intro / Opening (No Filter)
snippet.description:
Intro/opening of The King of Fighters '97: Global Match without using filters (scanlines or others). The King of Fighters '97: Global Match is a version of The King of Fighters '97 officially released for PC, Playstation 4 and PS Vita. The novelty is the possibility of online multiplayer.
Unfortunately, it's a version that doesn't allow you to select Orochi in any way, and it doesn't have a training mode.

#kof #kof97 #thekingoffighers
